            <thetext>The bug is reproducable with eg. the test in

application/demobrowser/source/html/test/Table_1.html

When clicking on the table the row remains with grey background.

By hitting the tab key the table is focusable and the background of the selected row changes to blue. In this state the table accepts key events.</thetext>
